Plot
The main character Gengobe ( Katsuo Nakamura ) , an exiled masterless samurai ( ronin ) , is facing a moral dilemma : use the money raised by his friends to either help a geisha he loves repay her supposed debts or , as intended , to fund his joining with his clan colleagues in a campaign of honor .
When the geisha and her hidden husband trick him out of his reinstatement money , Gengobe 's guilt and sense of betrayal drive him to extremes with wide consequences .
